column5: Hey did I fall asleep for 3 months and wake up in October? So much for fishing Simcoe this week!!!
Sunny hot & humid starting tomorrow though.
Lol ya we'll see Lew! Okay gotta go inside now my hands are freezing!!!

keep this in mind for next year, always and I mean always plan your holidays  begining July 1 - not before.  The weather gods just like Canada day -it never fails me.  Beauty weather Canada Day wknd and beyond and I'm off to donate blood to mosquitos starting tomorrow.
